<Rewrite PAsource="" >at </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >the High Court </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >yesterday.
</Rewrite>

<Verbatim PAsource="" >George Carman, QC, </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >counsel for </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >The Sun, </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >which </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >Mr Grobbelaar is suing </Verbatim>
