<Rewrite PAsource="" >legal </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >defence, </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >and vehemently maintained that his </New>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >career </Verbatim>
<New PAsource="" >was not over. </New>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >It was </Rewrite>
<Verbatim PAsource="" >untrue, </Verbatim>
<Rewrite PAsource="" >he said, that he had taken bribes and </Rewrite>
